description.undefined: An ontology for modeling educational institutions' funding, assessment, and student management systems. It captures the relationships between students, educational programs, funding mechanisms, and assessment processes. The ontology supports tracking student statuses, attendance, progression, and funding eligibility while maintaining compliance with educational standards and reporting requirements.

comments.undefined:
This ontology models:
    1. Student enrollment and status tracking
    2. Educational program structures and requirements
    3. Funding mechanisms and eligibility criteria
    4. Assessment and progression tracking
    5. Attendance monitoring systems
    6. Documentation and compliance requirements
    7. Administrative processes and support systems

coverage.value: Educational domain including student management, program administration, funding allocation, and assessment tracking.
